## Git Workflow

**`develop` is the default branch. `main` is production only.**

Conventional commits:
`feat|fix|test|refactor|chore|docs(scope): description`

```bash
# Push -- commit before pulling (rebase fails with dirty tree)
git add <files> && git commit -m "msg"
git pull --rebase && git push
```

Run verification sequentially with `;` or `&&`, never as parallel processes.

